des:
Ask Alexa for an interesting list of facts about RitaontheRocks™️ “The Rocks” Liquor or Cocktail of the your choice. Learn more then just the basics about the booze you consume! When using the “The Rocks” skill by RitaontheRocks , you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next fact. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
